Name: United Kingdom 10-year Inflation Indexed Bond Yield
Metadata:
Source: Bank of England

Inflation-adjusted bonds receive special tax treatment in the UK. Consequently, their yields are lower than the rates for inflation-adjusted bonds in other countries.
